区块链技术及其在铁路行业的典型应用研究
李 平1，张晓栋2，郭 悦1，谢 鹏2 
（1.中国铁道科学研究院集团有限公司，北京 100081； 2.中国铁道科学研究院集团有限公司 电子计算技术研究所，北京 100081） 摘 要：详细介绍区块链技术的定义、特征与关键技术，综合分析区块链技术的国内外应用现状 与政策发展趋势。提出铁路大数据共享、“一带一路”铁路货运物流等典型场景的区块链技术应用方 案，并从顶层设计、标准体系、典型应用、服务平台等方面给出了铁路区块链技术应用的相关建议。 关键词：铁路运输；区块链技术；典型应用；大数据共享；货运物流 中图分类号：U29 : TP39 文献标识码：A

Blockchain technology and its typical application in railway industry
LI Ping1, ZHANG Xiaodong2, GUO Yue1, XIE Peng2
( 1. China Academy of Railway Sciences Corporation Limited, Beijing  100081, China; 2.Institute of Computing Technologies, China Academy of Railway Sciences Corporation Limited, Beijing  100081, China )
Abstract: This paper introduced the definition, characteristics and key technologies of blockchain technology in detail, comprehensively analyzed the application status and policy development trend of the blockchain technology at home and abroad, put forward a blockchain technology application plan for railway big data sharing and "the Belt and Road" railway freight logistics and other typical scenes.The paper also given some suggestions on the application of railway blockchain technology from the aspects of top-level design, standard system, typical application, service platform, etc. Keywords: railway transport; blockchain technology; typical application; big data sharing; freight logistics

